<div class="jumbotron" id="about">
  <div class="container" id="home-content">
    <div class="row text-center">   
      <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1" id="headline">
        <h1>About FundWok</h1>
        <h2>Thank you for visiting us at this young stage of our development!</h2>
        <h3 id="subtitle">If you like the idea of making funding easy and would like to help us improve that process, please read on.</h3>
        <br />
        <%= link_to "#fw-intro", :class => "btn btn-danger btn-lg btn-start", :id => 'btn-readon' do %>
        	<span class="action-text">Read on</span>&nbsp;
        	<i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-down fa-2x action-icon"></i>
        <% end %>      
      </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container" id="fw-intro">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-1">
      <h3>What is FundWok?</h3>
    	<p>
    		FundWok is an innovative online social community where resources are located and shared effectively. It serves as a hub for great ideas and initiatives that are encouraged and supported. Simply put, FundWok is where established professionals or individuals make differences however they like. Our slogan is: “FundWok gives the freedom to fund whoever you want for whatever you want.” 
    	</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-1 text-center">
      <i class="fa fa-comments about-icon"></i>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /.row -->
</div>


<div class="container">

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-md-offset-1 text-center">
      <i class="fa fa-group about-icon"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4">
      <h3>
      	How does FundWok work?
      </h3>
      <p>
      	There is no limit to how many projects can be funded or what kind of projects they are. Companies can offer funds to grow or market their business in unique ways not available anywhere else online. Individuals can promote social causes, get assistance with projects, hire help for the day, and so on, as the possibilities are endless. 
      </p>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /.row -->

	<hr class="featurette-divider">

	<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-1">
      <h3>
        How is FundWok unique?
      </h3>
    	<p>
    		FundWok is unique in that it gives funders the freedom to choose how much to give and what conditions to set to giving without any commitments. 
    	</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-1 text-center">
      <i class="fa fa-magic" style="font-size: 10em;"></i>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /.row -->
  <br />
  <br />
</div>

<div class="jumbotron" id="about-action">
  <div class="container" id="about-action-headline">
    <div class="row text-center">   
			<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center">
        <h2>Join the exclusive community</h2>
        <h3>Before others do.</h3>
        <% if current_user %>
          <%= link_to new_post_path, :class => "btn btn-fw btn-action", :id => "about-add-new-fund" do %>
            <span class="btn-action-content">+ Add New Fund</span>
          <% end %>
        <% else %>
          <%= link_to "#myModal", :data => {:toggle=>"modal"}, :class => "btn btn-danger btn-lg btn-start", :id => "about-join-fw-btn" do %>
            <div id="about-join-fw-content">
          	 <i class='fa fa-user'></i>&nbsp;
          	 <span class="about-join-fw-text">Join fundwok<span style="vertical-align: super; font-size: 0.5em;">beta</span></span>
            </div>
          <% end %>  
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>